criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Higher than 18 years old;

          -  Undergoing hemodialysis for at least three months;

          -  Auditory acuity to listen to Mindfulness practices;

          -  Be interested in the objectives of this study and be randomized in one of the two
             groups (MBI or TAU).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Severe cognitive impairment or severe psychiatric disorder diagnosed by the medical
             staff of the nephrology unit;

          -  Suicidal ideation.
